'''Queen of Gondor''' was the title given to the spouse of the ruling [[King of Gondor]] (no Queen ruled [[Gondor]] in her own name at any time during its recorded history). The most famous Queens were [[Berúthiel]] (Queen to King [[Tarannon Falastur]]) and [[Arwen|Arwen Evenstar]], the consort of [[Aragorn|Aragorn Elessar]].
